{"tid":2204872,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚凌晨聯賽杯有西布朗對決超級神奇熱血公民球隊Harrogate(哈佬機)，大家萬勿錯過。","createTime":"2020-09-16T11:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T00:45:46.000Z","uid":73381,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d868481758930c953d2738f6279afd71b7cd3a97","tid":2204872,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n4zofJr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn4zofJr.jpg&h=a15989e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHarrogate 係上個月嘅全國聯賽升班附加賽 係溫布萊球場贏諾士郡3：1，歷史上首次升上EFL系統嘅英乙聯賽<br />\n<br />\n哈佬機最出名嘅球員係曾經效力暴力般流浪嘅Jon Stead <br />\n條撚樣當年同奇雲道理(另一條撚樣)並稱英超兩大神童鋒霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隊撚波上星期英乙第一戰就4：0大炒修安聯<br />\n今晚係佢哋隊史第一次迎戰英超球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對手係閪布朗，大家記得收睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885b50457d4e3349e5ab2ffc5d23866d0ef97ea6","tid":2204872,"uid":171273,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:12:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e069d7e0b511355298b5fc4ec4732377404f338a","tid":2204872,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"885b50457d4e3349e5ab2ffc5d23866d0ef97ea6","tid":2204872,"uid":171273,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:12:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254a1c27802027a0c23d6664da6dd0d3f52f1664","tid":2204872,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"885b50457d4e3349e5ab2ffc5d23866d0ef97ea6","tid":2204872,"uid":171273,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T11:12:29.000Z","msg":